<item>
            <title>[HBASE-332] Replace custom hbase locking with java.util.concurrent.locks.ReentrantLock</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-332</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HBase has a locking class that is effectively a clone of java.util.concurrent.locks.ReentrantLock.  This issue is about replacing HLocking with the java native implementation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12369862">HBASE-332</key>
            <summary>Replace custom hbase locking with java.util.concurrent.locks.ReentrantLock</summary>
